					"type": 23,
					"value": "When a player from a class other than a paladin tries to speak with the Oathbtreaker Knight he will not want to start a conversation.\r\nFrom design: Any non-paladin character talking to the Oathbreaker receives no reply. The Oathbreaker looks up at the character, but shakes their head - they have no interest in you."
